data.description: Roomy 3 bedroom 2.5 bath townhouse with a 2 car garage!  Living room is large with room for a desk area too.  Downstairs flooring is all tile.  Kitchen is bright with granite counters & stainless steel appliances, eat in dining area with xtra storage cabinets and granite.  Primary Bedroom has vaulted ceilings, 2 closets, double sinks with granite tops.  Also upstairs is 2 secondary bedrooms and another storage cabinet/counter area in the landing.  Seller offer $3k carpet allowance.  The upstairs AC unit was installed July 2022, it is a 2.5 ton Trane Split Heat Pump System with a 17 seer.  HOA covers water, garbage, exterior and roof.  Easy access to the loops101 & 202 plus ASU research park and Chandler Fashion Mall.  Short distance to highly rated CTA Goodman
